28/8/17 Wet nearly all day. Paid 1-9-4 (40 francs) ? making total debits 30-10-3
29/8/17 Rained heavily morning. Bull ring at 10.30am bayonet Bombing
30/8/17 Warned for draft for front. In tents all day ? rained slightly. Sent ppcards to England Australia.
31/8/17 Fall in 7.30am full marching order. Marched to Havre Stn to a troop train coming 11.45am. Left 4.30pm. Travelled via Yvetot, Motteville, Bosc-le-Hard, Carine, Serqueux, Abbeville, Conchil-le-Temple, St Josse, Etaples, Hesdigneul, Boulogne, Tentelleries, Wimereux, St Omer, Arques, Wizernes, Lumbres.
